name: GummiArm
tagline: A compliant and printable robot arm.
body:
![The GummiArm](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mstoelen/GummiArm/master/media/web/gummi_point.jpg)

Welcome to the GummiArm project! Checkout the [repository](https://github.com/mstoelen/GummiArm) for the latest code and printables.

Videos: https://plus.google.com/collection/oGXbV

Part of the DeCoRo project at Plymouth University: http://www.tech.plym.ac.uk/SoCCE/CRNS/decoro/

Older updates here: http://redskapsbua.com/blog/
